:02:40.000Z","msg":"獌同熱，邊忽有體力優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"獌的確有體力優勢喎, 仲要無傷兵full team<br />\n你有無睇過熱個地獄賽程同傷兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"頂龍未5-5波... <br />\n有冇睇過熱之前係咩對手 <br />\n同埋熱而家多人瘋狂輪休<br />\n獌之前場場比人禁屌到90分鐘...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲笑人冇睇賽程 笑撚死"},{"pid":"0b3fb856824b9752d0a1e6184d62b6fc9abe44ec","tid":2232981,"uid":59444,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"獌狗 真係好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人炒到1-6都多多藉口 好嘔心"},{"pid":"edf96dc764508b230810dbf8131c77286ff769dc","tid":2232981,"uid":170896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"219c9d2dc850f33b71448366d5e24fdd2ab3da2a","tid":2232981,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"未紅都1-2啦,當冇紅牌11打11,下半場摩佬泊大巴入條毛咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"對住曼洗唔洗拍大巴阿?諗多左啦"},{"pid":"be64ba006cfad080b08bf428af747ce2e89351f1","tid":2232981,"uid":88110,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:36:44.000Z","msg":"佢真心肉酸 成日叫人眼光唔好咁狹窄 <br />\n明明最唔聽人意見個個就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n估中左就幾年前既野都拎返出黎認屎認屁<br />\n估錯左就話人地靠運，靠個人能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩輪利物浦對阿仙奴，佢話阿仙奴坐和望贏，最後大家有眼睇，仲要覺得利物浦靠運贏，唔係羅拔臣送球比你，阿仙奴上半場攻門都無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好笑係d賽後評，例如賽果係2比1，有1球係靠運既，佢就會話如果唔係運氣，呢場就係1比1，大佬呀，一隊球隊即場會因為唔同比數而有唔同應對架嘛，點可以話無呢球個比數就1比1呀，佢識唔識踢波架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實講波講得好，用黎賺錢真心無問題，但唔好盲撐呀，班何粉盲撐到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 都聽得幾多球評節目，莫講話體野、理性呢d高質節目，連肥so文傑呢d 9upper都好過佢"},{"pid":"45908dade5ccaeacd171dedc219f8885a816a6e0","tid":2232981,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"11259c2e21482e21e7f22fe77a53bdbf9596c8c1","tid":2232981,"uid":59444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30df9ba392c1e37803505ccba7dce9c4877162e8","tid":2232981,"uid":91463,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f7d630f526efa53e70897adf3f9aadfa50e162c8","tid":2232981,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:02:40.000Z","msg":"獌同熱，邊忽有體力優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"獌的確有體力優勢喎, 仲要無傷兵full team<br />\n你有無睇過熱個地獄賽程同傷兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"頂龍未5-5波... <br />\n有冇睇過熱之前係咩對手 <br />\n同埋熱而家多人瘋狂輪休<br />\n獌之前場場比人禁屌到90分鐘...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲笑人冇睇賽程 笑撚死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"佢講賽程 無計表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df72efe1ef820670e31bdea52a3eeaa40ca9501","tid":2232981,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be64ba006cfad080b08bf428af747ce2e89351f1","tid":2232981,"uid":88110,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:36:44.000Z","msg":"佢真心肉酸 成日叫人眼光唔好咁狹窄 <br />\n明明最唔聽人意見個個就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n估中左就幾年前既野都拎返出黎認屎認屁<br />\n估錯左就話人地靠運，靠個人能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩輪利物浦對阿仙奴，佢話阿仙奴坐和望贏，最後大家有眼睇，仲要覺得利物浦靠運贏，唔係羅拔臣送球比你，阿仙奴上半場攻門都無啦<img src=\"/assets